ataḥ svacittam eva śakyaṃ vārayiṣyāmi. anyavāraṇasyāpārthakatvāt, svacittavāraṇād eva tatsiddheḥ. tasmāt sā cittam eva.

<commentary>vīryapāramitā tu kuśalotsāhasvabhāvātivispaṣṭaṃ cittam evety āha.

vacanakāyasahitasyāpi cittasya kuśalapakṣe mandapracārasya na tādṛśaṃ phalamupajāyate, yādṛśaṃ dhyānādiviṣaye paṭupravṛtter ekākino 'pi cittasya phalaṃ brahmabhūyādikam. tasmāt sā cittam eva.</commentary>

dhyānaṃ tu cittaikāgratālakṣaṇaṃ cittādanyathā vaktumaśakyamity āha-

mantrādyāvartanalakṣaṇā vacanavyāpārā japāḥ.